# Instagram recap video build — working directory.
# Heavy media (footage, title frames, audio, intermediates, the static ffmpeg
# binary, fonts, exports) is generated/downloaded at build time and NOT tracked.
# Only the pipeline source is committed.
scratchpad-video/*
!scratchpad-video/build_video.py
!scratchpad-video/build_audio.py
!scratchpad-video/README.md
!scratchpad-video/titles
scratchpad-video/titles/*
!scratchpad-video/titles/title.html
!scratchpad-video/titles/render_titles.py
